CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 15, 1954, pg. 36, reads: "Giants at YMCA Father-Son Banquet - Monte Irvin of the New York Giants, Curtis Roberts of the Pittsburgh Pirates and Willie Mays of the New York Giants are shown signing autographs last Saturday after they appeared at the YMCA's annual Father-Son Banquet, in the first photograph, top left... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Baseball players Willie Mays, Monte Irvin, and Curtis "Curt" Roberts signing autographs for boys in YMCA gymnasium
